        <Parent_String>waterfront spaces [300120792], waterfronts and waterfront spaces [300120789], open spaces by location or context [300008337], open spaces [300008072], Open Spaces and Site Elements (hierarchy name ) [300139081], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
